data.description: Welcome to 204 Cashmere Court, located in the gated neighborhood of Eagle Springs. You are going to love this all brick home! From the moment you walk in the two-story foyer, you will feel the warmth and love that is offered. On the main level, you will not only find one but two primary suites with tray ceilings. The newly renovated office with a reading nook, is perfect for working from home. The gourmet kitchen has granite and is a chef's dream. The upstairs has three bedrooms with two full baths, and a loft! Outside has a screened in porch with a fenced in yard. Neighborhood amenities include a water park, gym and tennis court!  Newer hvac and roof.
